The evidence with the title 'Obama unveils universal health care plan - CBS News ' says May 29, 2007  ... Obama said his plan could save the average consumer $ 2,500 a year and bring health care to all . Campaign aides estimated the cost of the program at $50 billion to $ 65 billion a year, financed largely by eliminating tax cuts that are scheduled to expire . President Bush wants to make those cuts permanent. 
